Brief installation instructions.
R-scape v0.1	   Feb 2016
http://selab.org
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Starting from a source distribution, R-scape_v0.1/:
 move into new directory:   cd R-scape_v0.1
 configure:                 ./configure
 build:                     make
 install:		    make install

The newly compiled binary "R-scape" is in the R-scape_v0.1/bin directory.
You can run it from there.

For complete documentation, see the R-scape User's Guide 
(R-scape_userguide.pdf).

The default installation produces executable: R-scape_v0.1/src/R-scape

